Combat Engine
Functionality:
1. Player to Enemy attack
2. Enemy to player Attack
3. Priority Queue based on speed for turns
4. Buff/Debuff System
5. Giving rewards at the end
6. Win/lose conditions based on health
7. return the player object


State Tracking
each section of states should be its own dictionary

Functionality:
1. Generic states for the main game that would control the world
2. states for each NPC eg. Greg, Arcade NPC, Inn NPC
3. Save/load functions - no need to fully define yet

Mini Game Controller
Functionality:
1. Call games with their own functions
2. Games will be imported 
3. Retreive game Scores
4. Update high score tables
5. Create High Score Tables
